@model HashTag.ViewModels.GrowthTrackerViewModel
@using Microsoft.Extensions.Localization
@using HashTag
@using HashTag.Helpers
@inject IStringLocalizer<SharedResource> Localizer
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = Localizer["Growth_PageTitle"];
    ViewData["Description"] = Localizer["Growth_PageDescription"];
    ViewData["Keywords"] = Localizer["Growth_PageKeywords"];
    Layout = "_LayoutPublic";

    var currentRegion = Context.Request.Cookies["UserRegion"] ?? "VN";
    var isVietnamese = currentRegion == "VN";
}

<div class="container py-4">
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-gradient">
                <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow me-2"></i> @Localizer["Growth_Title"]
            </h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted">@Localizer["Growth_Subtitle"]</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Category Filter -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold">
                        <i class="bi bi-funnel me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_FilterCategory"]
                    </label>
                    <select id="categoryFilter" class="form-select" onchange="filterByCategory(this.value)">
                        <option value="">@Localizer["Growth_AllCategories"]</option>
                        @foreach (var category in Model.Categories)
                        {
                            var displayName = isVietnamese && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(category.DisplayNameVi)
                                ? category.DisplayNameVi
                                : category.Name;
                            @if (category.Id == Model.SelectedCategoryId)
                            {
                                <option value="@category.Slug" selected>@displayName</option>
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <option value="@category.Slug">@displayName</option>
                            }
                        }
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SEO Content Section -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 bg-light">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff-fill"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">@Localizer["Growth_Feature1_Title"]</h6>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                    @Localizer["Growth_Feature1_Desc"]
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">@Localizer["Growth_Feature2_Title"]</h6>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                    @Localizer["Growth_Feature2_Desc"]
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">@Localizer["Growth_Feature3_Title"]</h6>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                    @Localizer["Growth_Feature3_Desc"]
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fastest Growing Section -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-header bg-gradient-primary text-white">
                    <h4 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_FastestGrowing"]
                    </h4>
                    <small>@Localizer["Growth_FastestGrowingDesc"]</small>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    @if (Model.FastestGrowing.Any())
                    {
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            @foreach (var hashtag in Model.FastestGrowing)
                            {
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="growth-card fastest-growing" onclick="window.open('/hashtag/@hashtag.Tag', '_blank')">
                                        <div class="growth-header">
                                            <div class="hashtag-tag">#@hashtag.Tag</div>
                                            <span class="badge bg-info">@hashtag.CategoryName</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-stats">
                                            <div class="growth-percentage text-success">
                                                <span class="growth-icon">@hashtag.GrowthIcon</span>
                                                <span class="percentage-value">+@hashtag.GrowthPercentage.ToString("N1")%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="growth-status-badge @GetStatusClass(hashtag.GrowthStatus)">
                                                @hashtag.GrowthStatus
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-metrics">
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-eye me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentViews)</span>
                                                <span class="metric-change text-success">+@FormatNumber(hashtag.ViewsIncrease)</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-file-post me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentPosts)</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-recommendation">
                                            <small class="text-muted">@hashtag.RecommendationNote</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_NoGrowthData"]
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trending Growth Section -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-header bg-gradient-success text-white">
                    <h4 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-fire me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_TrendingGrowth"]
                    </h4>
                    <small>@Localizer["Growth_TrendingGrowthDesc"]</small>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    @if (Model.TrendingGrowth.Any())
                    {
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            @foreach (var hashtag in Model.TrendingGrowth)
                            {
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="growth-card trending" onclick="window.open('/hashtag/@hashtag.Tag', '_blank')">
                                        <div class="growth-header">
                                            <div class="hashtag-tag">#@hashtag.Tag</div>
                                            <span class="badge bg-info">@hashtag.CategoryName</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-stats">
                                            <div class="growth-percentage @(hashtag.GrowthPercentage >= 0 ? "text-success" : "text-danger")">
                                                <span class="growth-icon">@hashtag.GrowthIcon</span>
                                                <span class="percentage-value">@(hashtag.GrowthPercentage >= 0 ? "+" : "")@hashtag.GrowthPercentage.ToString("N1")%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="growth-status-badge @GetStatusClass(hashtag.GrowthStatus)">
                                                @hashtag.GrowthStatus
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-metrics">
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-eye me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentViews)</span>
                                                <span class="metric-change @(hashtag.ViewsIncrease >= 0 ? "text-success" : "text-danger")">
                                                    @(hashtag.ViewsIncrease >= 0 ? "+" : "")@FormatNumber(hashtag.ViewsIncrease)
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-file-post me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentPosts)</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-recommendation">
                                            <small class="text-muted">@hashtag.RecommendationNote</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_NoTrendingData"]
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Declining Section -->
    @if (Model.Declining.Any())
    {
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-header bg-gradient-warning text-white">
                        <h4 class="mb-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-graph-down-arrow me-2"></i>@Localizer["Growth_Declining"]
                        </h4>
                        <small>@Localizer["Growth_DecliningDesc"]</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            @foreach (var hashtag in Model.Declining)
                            {
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="growth-card declining" onclick="window.open('/hashtag/@hashtag.Tag', '_blank')">
                                        <div class="growth-header">
                                            <div class="hashtag-tag">#@hashtag.Tag</div>
                                            <span class="badge bg-info">@hashtag.CategoryName</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-stats">
                                            <div class="growth-percentage text-danger">
                                                <span class="growth-icon">@hashtag.GrowthIcon</span>
                                                <span class="percentage-value">@hashtag.GrowthPercentage.ToString("N1")%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="growth-status-badge badge-declining">
                                                @hashtag.GrowthStatus
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-metrics">
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-eye me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentViews)</span>
                                                <span class="metric-change text-danger">@FormatNumber(hashtag.ViewsIncrease)</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="metric">
                                                <i class="bi bi-file-post me-1"></i>
                                                <span class="metric-value">@FormatNumber(hashtag.CurrentPosts)</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="growth-recommendation">
                                            <small class="text-muted">@hashtag.RecommendationNote</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    }
</div>

@functions {
    private string FormatNumber(long number)
    {
        if (number >= 1000000000)
            return $"{number / 1000000000.0:F1}B";
        if (number >= 1000000)
            return $"{number / 1000000.0:F1}M";
        if (number >= 1000)
            return $"{number / 1000.0:F1}K";
        return number.ToString();
    }

    private string GetStatusClass(string status)
    {
        return status switch
        {
            "Bùng nổ" => "badge-explosion",
            "Đang lên mạnh" => "badge-rising",
            "Tăng trưởng ổn định" => "badge-stable-growth",
            "Ổn định" => "badge-stable",
            "Giảm" => "badge-slight-decline",
            "Đang giảm" => "badge-declining",
            _ => "badge-neutral"
        };
    }
}

<style>
    .feature-box {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .feature-box h6 {
        color: #2d3748;
    }

    .bg-gradient-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    }

    .bg-gradient-success {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
    }

    .bg-gradient-warning {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffa751 0%, #ffe259 100%);
    }

    .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .growth-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
        height: 100%;
        border-left: 4px solid transparent;
    }

    .growth-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .growth-card.fastest-growing {
        border-left-color: #667eea;
    }

    .growth-card.fastest-growing:hover {
        border-left-color: #764ba2;
    }

    .growth-card.trending {
        border-left-color: #f5576c;
    }

    .growth-card.trending:hover {
        border-left-color: #f093fb;
    }

    .growth-card.declining {
        border-left-color: #ffa751;
    }

    .growth-card.declining:hover {
        border-left-color: #ffe259;
    }

    .growth-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hashtag-tag {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #2d3748;
        word-break: break-word;
        flex: 1;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .growth-stats {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .growth-percentage {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .growth-icon {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .growth-status-badge {
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge-explosion {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
    }

    .badge-rising {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #84fab0 0%, #8fd3f4 100%);
        color: #1a202c;
    }

    .badge-stable-growth {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea 0%, #fed6e3 100%);
        color: #1a202c;
    }

    .badge-stable {
        background: #e2e8f0;
        color: #4a5568;
    }

    .badge-slight-decline {
        background: #fef5e7;
        color: #f39c12;
    }

    .badge-declining {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffa751 0%, #ffe259 100%);
        color: #1a202c;
    }

    .growth-metrics {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding: 0.75rem;
        background: #f7fafc;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .metric {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .metric-value {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
    }

    .metric-change {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-left: auto;
    }

    .growth-recommendation {
        padding-top: 0.75rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .growth-recommendation small {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        display: block;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .growth-percentage {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .growth-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hashtag-tag {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<!-- Localization data for JavaScript -->
<div id="jsLocalization" class="d-none"
    data-growth-url="@LocalizedUrlHelper.GetGrowthTrackingUrl(Context)">
</div>

<script>
    const localization = document.getElementById('jsLocalization').dataset;

    function filterByCategory(catSlug) {
        const baseUrl = localization.growthUrl;
        const url = catSlug ? `${baseUrl}/${catSlug}` : baseUrl;
        window.location.href = url;
    }
</script>
